verbose_text: But, differences in costs for each group between 100-days and 30-days time horizon in ICU lead us to conclude that CHG-T1 solution could induce savings owing to the highest difference in cost between the two time horizons studied, euro-3,026 for CHG-T1 group, euro-2,999 for PVI-T1 group, euro-2,955 for PVI-T4 group, and euro-2,241 for CHG-T4 group.
